        "content": "12 min AMRAP of:\n* Chest to ground Bear Crawl over the barbell x 2\n* Barbell Hang Power Snatch x 4\n* Overhead Squat (OHS) x2\nChest touches the ground before the barbell, bear crawl over the bar, touch chest to ground, crawl backwards over the bar, touch chest to ground. This is 1 rep.\nBarbell Loads\nRx: 35/45 kg\nSc1: 30/35 kg\nSc2: 25/35 kg",
